<div class="text">
    <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Being part of a gang unlocks new possibilities and introduces you to a realm of activities that are often prohibited by law. Some of these activities include, but are not limited to: <strong>robbery</strong>, <strong>thefts</strong>, <strong>war for territory</strong>, <strong>arms and drug trafficking</strong>.</span></p>
    <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In total, 5 gangs can be found in the state: <strong>Blood Street Gang</strong>, <strong>The Families</strong>, <strong>The Ballas Gang</strong>, <strong>Los Santos Vagos</strong>, <strong>Marabunta Grande</strong>. Just like the mafias, some of them may be in alliance, and some of them may wage bitter wars.</span></p>
    <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">One of the main tasks of each gang - <strong>control of the largest number of territories</strong>, for each of them they receive $90. Therefore, there is a war for territory between the gangs, after the start of the war, the main task of the gang is to destroy all their opponents.</span></p>
    <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Illegal items, crucial for facilitating robberies, kidnappings, and other criminal endeavors, can be procured by the gang members through clandestine channels and underground markets. "<strong>black market</strong>"</span></p>
    <p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Recruitment</strong> Prospective individuals interested in joining a gang undergo a rigorous application process, where it is essential to adhere to the organization's internal rules and regulations without fail.</span></p>
    <p><strong>Commands</strong>
        <br /><strong>/follow</strong> - to lead
        <br /><strong>/openstock</strong> - open a warehouse
        <br /><strong>/closestock</strong> - close the warehouse
        <br /><strong>/capture</strong> - start capturing territory
        <br /><strong>/tpcapture</strong> - teleport to the capture area</p>
